<inglise> Having regard to Council Regulation (EEC) No 879/73 (2) of 26 March 1973 on the granting and reimbursement of aids accorded by the Member States to recognized producer groups in the hop sector, and in particular Article 5 (2) thereof; </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse n&otilde;ukogu 26. m&auml;rtsi 1973. aasta m&auml;&auml;rust (EM&Uuml;) nr 879/73 humalasektori tunnustatud tootjate &uuml;hendustele liikmesriikide poolt antava abi andmise ja tagastamise kohta, eriti selle artikli 5 l&otilde;iget 2, </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas Regulation (EEC) No 879/73 requires that the administrative costs to be taken into consideration in calculating the maximum amount of aid granted to recognized producer groups in order to encourage their formation and facilitate their operation shall be determined, and whereas it is necessary to define the said costs; </inglise>
